rina Karnus</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/lothar-baumgarte/" rel="tag">Lothar Baumgarte</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/motti-kaston/" rel="tag">Motti Kastn</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/nina-von-mechow/" rel="tag">Nina von Mechow</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/richard-wagner/" rel="tag">Richard Wagner</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/sergio-morabito/" rel="tag">Sergio Morabito</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/shigeo-ishino/" rel="tag">Shigeo Ishino</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/staatsoper-stuttgart/" rel="tag">Staatsoper Stuttgart</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/sylvain-cambreling/" rel="tag">Sylvain Cambreling</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/torsten-hoffmann/" rel="tag">Torsten Hoffmann</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/tristan-und-isolde/" rel="tag">Tristan und Isolde</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Andr Morsch, Attila Jun, Bert Neumann, Daniel Kluge, Jossi Wieler, Katarina Karnus, Lothar Baumgarte, Motti Kastn, Nina von Mechow, Opera lirica, Richard Wagner, Sergio Morabito, Shigeo Ishino, Staatsoper Stuttgart, Sylvain Cambreling, Torsten Hoffmann, Tristan und Isolde"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/e15610f34674f02caf174515ea5136d4" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/Mussomeli1-132x200.jpg" width="66" height="100" alt="Gianguido Mussomeli" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Gianguido Mussomeli"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/gianguido-mussomeli/">View all articles by Gianguido Mussomeli</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/07/jonas-kaufmann-e-helmut-deutsch-al-munchner-opernfestspiele-2014/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Jonas Kaufmann e Helmut Deutsch al Mnchner Opernfestspiele 2014</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/07/napa-valley-festival-del-sole-bella-italia-opera-gala/" rel="next">Napa Valley, Festival del Sole,&#8221; Bella Italia! Opera Gala&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 1 comment</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-35200"> <article id="comment-35200" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/c5946d8bec06b2978e478f17e2381e02?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn"><a href=\'http://laulilla.wordpress.com\' rel=\'external nofollow\' class=\'url\'>laulilla</a></cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/07/staatsoper-stuttgarttristan-und-isolde/#comment-35200"><time datetime="2014-07-22T20:18:53+00:00">22 luglio 2014 at 20:18</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comme